title: Ep. 382 - National Suicide Squad
description:
The four horsewomen of our political apocalypse—Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez, Ilhan Omar, Rashida Tlaib, and Ayanna Pressley—have given themselves a new nickname. Then, more men beat women at women’s sports, Biden’s campaign keeps going nowhere, and Al Green proposes a convenient strategy to redeem America for her “original sin.” Date: 07-16-2019
